CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: US Goldmining Inc is a mineral exploration and development company. It is a focused on the exploration and development of a project located in Alaska, USA. The company's sole property is Whistler Project which is a gold-copper exploration project located in the Yentna Mining District, approximately 150 km northwest of Anchorage, Alaska.
